<subSubSection id="02DF919DE28FF266E42A341C299802A0" pageId="0" pageNumber="139" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="DE11BAE12E5DF8D4FD8F4C25E51CFC5C" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Biology.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="BFC081636C45B348D35D9F9A1BF3725D" pageId="0" pageNumber="139">Mountainous species (1900-2500 m a.s.l.) with flight period in autumn. Adults are attracted by light.</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
